[src:chicken-scheme/compiler] In subsequent years several C++ compilers were developed as C++ popularity grew.
[src:chicken-scheme/compiler] In many application domains, the idea of using a higher-level language quickly caught on.
[src:chicken-scheme/compiler] Because of the expanding functionality supported by newer programming languages and the increasing complexity of computer architectures, compilers became more complex.
