[src:chicken-scheme/compiler] The Production Quality Compiler-Compiler PQCC design would produce a Production Quality Compiler (PQC) from formal definitions of source language and the target.
[src:chicken-scheme/compiler] PQCC tried to extend the term compiler-compiler beyond the traditional meaning as a parser generator (e.g., Yacc) without much success.
[src:chicken-scheme/compiler] PQCC might more properly be referred to as a compiler generator.
