[src:chicken-scheme/compiler] The effort discovered and designed the phase structure of the PQC.
[src:chicken-scheme/compiler] The BLISS-11 compiler provided the initial structure.
[src:chicken-scheme/compiler] The phases included analyses (front end), intermediate translation to virtual machine (middle end), and translation to the target (back end).
[src:chicken-scheme/compiler] TCOL was developed for the PQCC research to handle language specific constructs in the intermediate representation.
[src:chicken-scheme/compiler] Variations of TCOL supported various languages.
[src:chicken-scheme/compiler] The PQCC project investigated techniques of automated compiler construction.
